  • Method Details

    • of

      public static Request of(String url) throws IOException, InterruptedException, URISyntaxException
      Main access point of this API. Creates a Request given the RaiPlay URL. Grabs all the needed information from the RaiPlay website (parsing their JSON) and returns a new Request object accordingly.
      Parameters:
      url - the URL of the RaiPlay title.
      Returns:
      a Request object with all the needed information grabbed automatically from RaiPlay.
      Throws:
      IOException - if an error occurs when sending HTTP requests.
      InterruptedException - if the operation is interrupted.
      URISyntaxException - if the URL provided is invalid.

    • ofAll

      public static List<Request> ofAll(String titleUrl) throws IOException, URISyntaxException, InterruptedException
      Creates a List of Requests to be processed in parallel. It is useful to download all episodes of a TV show.
      Parameters:
      titleUrl - the URL of the main TV show RaiPlay page.
      Returns:
      a List<Request> of all successfully created requests.
      Throws:
      IOException - if an I/O exception in parsing occurs.
      URISyntaxException - if the provided URL is malformed.
      InterruptedException - if the operation is interrupted.

    • submit

      public Downloader submit(String outputDir)
      Creates a Downloader object (an implementation of Runnable) and returns it.
      Parameters:
      outputDir - the path of the directory to save the video file to.
      Returns:
      a Downloader representing the task "Download the video contained in this Request".
